DOC.HEADLINE: J.F.K. PAPERS
DOC.TEXT: I am not a fan of conspiracy theories . Nevertheless , I was amazed that in your Associated Press article ( " Graphic J.F.K. Assassination Car Photos , Records Released , " May 4 ) the definite statement is made that the released documents " shed little additional light on the assassination. " This conclusion was reached one day after 50 # 000 documents in 224 boxes were released to the public . JACK McNALLY Glendale
